BUEHNE STEEL WOOL CO. v. UNITED STATES. (Circuit Court of Appeals, Second Circuit. March 16, 1906). No. 191 (3924). Appeal from the Circuit Court of the United States for the Southern District of Now York. E'er decision below, see 140 Fed. 772.

Before WALLACE, LACQMBE, and TOWNSEND, Circuit .Judges.

PER CURIAM.

Affirmed in open court, on consent.
